  "title": "Lady of the White Moon",
  "description": "Many old legends speak of the Lady of the White Moon, an ancient being who slumbers in a vast palace on one of Erden's moons.\n\nIt is said that if one were to visit her there, she would rise from her sleep and offer the visitor a prophecy of their future. Most of Erden's mythical heroes are said to have received advice from her, aiding them in fulfilling their grand destinies.\n\nHowever, these legends offer no hints as to how to get to her palace in the first place. Various plans have been devised, such as building some kind of flying machine or creating a powerful teleportation spell, but only a handful of eccentrics have actually attempted them. Most become discouraged by recurring dreams of their plans failing, often in an extremely spectacular fashion.",
